name: VSAccountMetadata
desc: A collection of information for a subscriber’s account.

items.name: var accountProviderIdentifier: String?
items.desc: The unique identifier of the account provider.

items.name: var authenticationExpirationDate: Date?
items.desc: The date when the user’s current authentication session expires.

items.name: var accountProviderResponse: VSAccountProviderResponse?
items.desc: The response from the account provider.

items.name: var samlAttributeQueryResponse: String?
items.desc: The SAML response from the account provider.

items.name: var verificationData: Data?
items.desc: Data you use to verify that the response came from the account provider.
